item.title: Speaker at Collab365
item.author: vbiret+blog@outlook.com (Vincent Biret)
item.description: I’ve been greatly honored being selected to be speaker at collab 365. This event directly comes from the sp24 with the spbiz which happened a few months from now. It’s a free online event which will take place on October the 8th during 24 hours all around the globe.
